<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="About SPMJ Foundation — our mission, story, and values in bringing education to every child." />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
</head>
<body data-page="<%= page %>">
  <%- include('header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">About SPMJ Foundation</span>
        <h1 class="display">We believe education is a <span class="grad">right</span>,<br />not a privilege.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          SPMJ Foundation began with a simple conviction: that no child's future
          should be decided by where they were born or what their family can
          afford. We exist to close that gap — one learner at a time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container two-col">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Our story</span>
          <h2>From one classroom to a movement.</h2>
          <p>
            SPMJ Foundation was started by a small group of teachers and
            volunteers who kept meeting bright, eager children with nowhere to
            learn. Families wanted education for their kids — but fees, distance,
            and daily survival kept getting in the way.
          </p>
          <p>
            So we opened a single free learning centre under a borrowed roof.
            Word spread, families came, and children stayed. Today that one room
            has grown into a network of centres, scholarships, and digital labs —
            but our promise is unchanged: learning should be free, joyful, and
            within every child's reach.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-art">
          <div class="story-card">
            <strong>2018</strong>
            <span>SPMJ Foundation begins with one free learning centre and 30 children.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="story-card">
            <strong>2021</strong>
            <span>First digital lab and scholarship programme launched.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="story-card">
            <strong>2024</strong>
            <span>Reached 5,000+ children across 40 learning centres.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="story-card">
            <strong>Today</strong>
            <span>A growing team of educators, volunteers, and supporters working for every child.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Our mission</h3>
            <p>To provide free, quality education and holistic support to underprivileged children, so they can break the cycle of poverty through learning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Our vision</h3>
            <p>A world where every child — regardless of income, gender, or background — has equal access to the education they need to shape their own future.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Our approach</h3>
            <p>We support the whole child: schooling, nutrition, digital skills, and mentoring — working alongside families and local communities, not apart from them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <span class="eyebrow">What we believe</span>
          <h2>The values that shape our work.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Every child matters</h3>
            <p>We meet children where they are and believe in every one of them — no learner is written off, ever.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Education is a right</h3>
            <p>Learning should never depend on a family's income. Our programs are free and open to all.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Dignity first</h3>
            <p>We serve with respect, never charity that shames. Children and families are partners, not recipients.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Transparency &amp; trust</h3>
            <p>Open reporting and honest numbers. Every supporter can see exactly how their contribution is used.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Rooted in community</h3>
            <p>Our teachers and volunteers come from the same neighbourhoods as our students. Change grows from within.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>In it for the long run</h3>
            <p>We walk with children from their first lessons to higher education and beyond. Real change takes years.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section cta-section">
      <div class="container cta-card">
        <div>
          <h2>Want to be part of the change?</h2>
          <p class="lead">Donate, volunteer, or simply learn more — we'd love to hear from you.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get involved →</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('footer') %>
  <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
